00:00:49.540 --> 00:00:52.548
So please welcome Svante Paabo.

00:00:52.548 --> 00:00:56.260
[APPLAUSE]

00:00:56.260 --> 00:00:58.545
SVANTE PAABO: OK, so do
that afterwards if you think

00:00:58.545 --> 00:01:03.320
it's-- So, yeah, what I wanted
to do though was then talk

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:06.730
a bit about what we can learn
about the origins of modern

00:01:06.730 --> 00:01:10.520
humans, so the origins of the
type of humans that exist all

00:01:10.520 --> 00:01:13.640
