00:44:00.340 --> 00:44:02.970
know.

00:44:02.970 --> 00:44:07.330
There are typical chemical
modifications of the old DNA.

00:44:07.330 --> 00:44:11.060
And in some specimens, most of
the bacteria have such things.

00:44:11.060 --> 00:44:14.040
So they are at least
thousands of years old.

00:44:14.040 --> 00:44:15.750
But we don't know
how much of that

00:44:15.750 --> 00:44:20.735
